sep.gaia.util

Class IntegerVector3D

  • java.lang.Object
    • sep.gaia.util.IntegerVector3D
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Vector3D

    public class IntegerVector3D
extends java.lang.Object
implements Vector3D
    Class to implement a 3-dimensional integer vector for a variety of purposes. Instances of this class may also be used as 2-dimensional vectors by using only the first two coordinates x and y and setting the z-coordinate on 0.
    Author:
    Max Witzelsperger
